Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.49,0:00:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lying in a strong heart is the power of deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.29,0:00:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stepping into the truth with a sharp rhythm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been a while since we heard from the police department.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excitement builds in an ominous case!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.38,0:00:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child and intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.30,0:00:32.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.50,0:01:51.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:52.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:54.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for not answering.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My cell phone's battery ran out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just got out of the car—I'm in a phone booth now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.39,0:02:06.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be at your place in about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye, see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:36.34,Title,,0,0,0,,MEGURE'S SEALED SECRET\N(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:42.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, how's this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a present for Kyogoku-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little cute for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:49.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.89,0:02:51.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's him...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:55.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This simple one will suit him just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No it won't, it's not hand-knit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It needs to be hand-knit?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:01.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I just thought a hand-knit \Nsweater would feel warm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.04,0:03:19.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I unintentionally mentioned it in\N the letter I sent him earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Right now, I'm knitting a sweater for someone I like."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:27.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never expected it to be so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.10,0:03:35.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were going to buy him a hand-knit\N sweater from a store and say you knit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.57,0:03:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't know how to knit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:45.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I admire your bravery in admitting that you\N like him, so I'll keep your secret to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.91,0:03:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I still haven't told Makoto-san that I like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you say so in the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm knitting for someone I like"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:59.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop beating around the bush or Kyogoku-san \Nmight think there's someone else you love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.88,0:04:03.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, that's the whole point!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.39,0:04:08.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto-san will definitely panic a\N bit when that comes to mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one day, a package will arrive at his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.10,0:04:16.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would think, "What is this, something \Nfrom Sonoko-san?" or something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.48,0:04:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And as he anxiously starts\N to open up the package...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Surprise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The sweater was actually for you! "
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.11,0:04:27.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you think of my marvelous love-love plan?{Funny: OCR read it as Lie-love plan, it was so good that I honestly wanted to keep it.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't come crying to me if he's not impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.79,0:04:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto-san won't express his feelings, so I don't \Nknow how he actually feels if I don't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.38,0:04:43.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know that he worries about me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still need the courage to ask him directly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.89,0:04:54.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, Ran, do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How Shinichi-kun feels about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:04:59.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:02.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.61,0:05:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to ask him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've known him since we were little, so it'd\N be a lie to say I don't want to know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:15.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.71,0:05:20.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"But, but, but, but, but, but, but, but, but...!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:24.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"l want to ask, but I'm afraid to know the answer."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"That's how I feel right now."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:31.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet you're thinking something dreamy like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.10,0:05:33.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:40.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I go to the parking garage and wait with Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tell Dad to go ahead and wait in the pasta\N house behind this department store, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, how about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems I've come across some idle\N girl-talk that I shouldn't have..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that one's too tasteless!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.92,0:05:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:09.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do girls like to spend so much time\N shopping and chatting on the phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.51,0:06:10.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So true...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.60,0:06:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this cold and she's wearing a mini-skirt that short?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How sexy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a ballpoint pen over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it belonged to that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.99,0:06:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, a great opportunity!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think this belongs to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:47.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Arrest him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:05.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Disguised in order to investigate the cases of\N the women who were attacked this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we asked Detective\N Satou to dress that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, the announcements said the\N suspect is about 150 cm tall...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.37,0:07:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A quick look at me will tell you I'm\N not the suspect! you're looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:22.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:26.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that attitude you had as you\N approached Satou-san was, uhm,..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:28.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I say "very special"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt I was in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:33.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it is tough to investigate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:46.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, since the only common link between the women\N was that they were all wearing fashionable clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:49.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even the crime scenes are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could we see the photos of those three women again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.24,0:08:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first one who was attacked\N is named Mizutani Ryouko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One night two weeks ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:07.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While she,was waiting in her car for the traffic\N light to change, another car rear-ended her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:12.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as she left the vehicle to complain,\Nshe was attacked with a metal bat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The next one to be attacked was Endou Hitomi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:22.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten nights ago, she was struck by a metal bat as she\N was coming out of a public restroom in a park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:26.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we have the one from last\N night, Ishiguro Michiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:30.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, she was attacked after\N coming out of a phone booth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said phone booth... Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.90,0:08:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was where we subdued you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fortunately, the lives of those \Nthree victims aren't in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.87,0:08:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They just share nothing in common other than\N the fashionable garb they were wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three said they\N hadn't made any enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that, Mouri-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Think of anything yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.88,0:08:56.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, one thing I noticed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.18,0:08:58.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One thing you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of them are mixed-race - like\N they grew up in a jungle or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:13.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it, they\N aren't normal Japanese people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:14.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, how cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:16.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These three ganguro look amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one in the middle is gonguro, so she's even darker.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This style is called Yamanba, and it's really\N fashionable among girls these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:27.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yamanba?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.17,0:09:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be you don't know, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:33.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, Yamanba!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.38,0:09:34.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know something that obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Ran-neechan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, she said she was going to the restroom and\N wanted me to meet her at this pasta house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:49.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if this was a series of random\N attacks, there's nothing we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:51.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.52,0:09:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To now, there haven't been any cases like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:56.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there was one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:10:00.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a string of female high school\N students being run over by cars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:02.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pretty disturbing cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.37,0:10:06.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm certain it was before I became a police detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At any rate, we should get back to investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:11.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case! I'll go back to being a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.67,0:10:15.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, a decoy is no longer necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Start over and investigate whether or not the three victims had any connection to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Mouri-kun, sorry about what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.10,0:10:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.57,0:10:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't find the exit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The, underground parking garage?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:44.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, you have no sense of direction, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko-neechan, about your\N ring, necklace, and bracelet...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't they look like those worn\N by the women in the photos?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.50,0:10:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where'd you buy them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.17,0:10:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't buy them, they were complimentary gifts\N from that department store we just went to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're having this Millennium Sale, \Nand they check your receipt at the exit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For every 10,000 yen you spend, you\N get to choose one of the accessories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're wearing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:14.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although they aren't wearing the entire set, they\N each have a piece that matches Sonoko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means these three...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:20.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are all customers of that department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:22.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.20,0:11:25.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Answer me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Ran!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.30,0:11:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:46.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:49.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a girl whose face is covered in blood!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim is Aizawa Tae-san, 20 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until one year ago, she worked in this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's been unemployed since.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:12.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So our fourth case is a murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same suspect, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.58,0:12:15.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.88,0:12:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We never announced the common\N characteristics of the victims to the public...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.50,0:12:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this is the parking garage of\N that same department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no denying the connection.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:29.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, this was done by someone bearing a grudge against this department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:29.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:30.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He claimed to have been waiting \Nfor her in the department store.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:43.53,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,His father is the owner of this department store...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:45.66,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa Noriyuki (24)\NCook
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:48.28,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And he planned to introduce his girlfriend\N at the restaurant where he works.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's a waitress who works in the\N same restaurant that he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:59.84,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Konno Yuri (24)\NWaitress
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.66,0:12:56.50,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Her name is Konno Yuri-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:13:00.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,She said they've been friends since college,\Nand that she sometimes gives him advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.17,0:13:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Advice?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.59,0:13:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa-san's father opposed his\N engagement with the deceased Aizawa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anyone suspicious\N when you found the body?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.10,0:13:18.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only person I passed by was the guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.94,0:13:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the guard standing by the entrance when I\N came down — a man who was about 40 years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:27.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that would be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.37,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I left my post in order to head to the restroom, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.66,0:13:34.29,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Sadakane Yoshio (43)\NGuard
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.29,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The culprit must have got to her while I wasn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:37.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is, if you aren't really the culprit yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.79,0:13:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:45.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall correctly, you worked at a rival\N department store until half a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:51.35,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Could you have arranged with your former employer to\N cause a scandal here and send my coustomers his way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:51.35,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Shirakawa Haruyoshi (53)\NHaido Department Store Owner
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.77,0:13:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at least now Noriyuki can get a new girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.69,0:14:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This time, how about finding\N a nice girl with a clean slate?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.82,0:14:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriyuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.07,0:14:10.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm, what did he mean by "clean slate"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.91,0:14:17.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's probably referring to the automobile accident she\N was involved in a year ago, in this parking garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.66,0:14:18.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Automobile accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.17,0:14:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She ran over a little boy, and after\N that accident, she gave up her job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yumi from the traffic division told me about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy was waiting in this parking garage for his\N mother when he stepped in front of a car and was hit
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:41.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The driver was going at a slow speed considering\N it was the inside of a parking garage, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, the boy's vitals were\N hit, and he died three days later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think the boy's name was Sakurai Akira,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.70,0:14:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Noriyuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.49,0:14:56.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know how tall your father is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:59.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A little over 150 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the rest of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,173 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.00,0:15:06.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm 144 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.96,0:15:08.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I'm 167
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:12.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Things aren't looking good for the owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.80,0:15:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would've known when she would be by her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.73,0:15:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was your father already at the\N restaurant when you arrived?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.48,0:15:30.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he didn't show up on time, so\N I asked her to see if he was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.28,0:15:32.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.99,0:15:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you be implying that my father is a suspect!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:43.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, we only asked because the other victims told\N us the culprit's height was around 150 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "other victims"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, as I thought, this is the work of that\N serial attacker we've been hearing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.17,0:15:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What have you done about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even know the culprit's height,\Nso why can't you catch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:16:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had caught the culprit, Tae wouldn't be dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Noriyuki-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:05.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tae is dead, and it's the fault of the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.40,0:16:07.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You police are all useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Noriyuki-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.82,0:16:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Useless
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You police are all useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.21,0:16:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.92,0:16:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said I was going to play decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guess...It didn't go smoothly like in the movies...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.97,0:16:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:43.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My apologies, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.49,0:16:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noriyuki-kun just went a little overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:01.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What he said was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, it might be best for\N him to go cool off for a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.79,0:17:07.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll return to my post.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.39,0:17:19.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did all three of those ladies attest that\N the culprit's height was around 150 cm?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:30.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, only the first and third victims said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The second victim was suddenly attacked from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was unconscious until a passerby found her,\N so she didn't catch a glimpse of her assailant.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, both that did say were certain\N that the culprit was about 150 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we called them down to the\N station a few days after the attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.71,0:17:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both stated that their attacker was\N roughly the same height as they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how tall were those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:54.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.80,0:17:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The first was 151 cm, and the third was 153 cm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.18,0:18:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We measured them at the station, \Nso there's no doubt about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell a kid too much about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.40,0:18:16.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:20.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.87,0:18:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I ran around looking for the exit, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:27.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, don't you think something's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.67,0:18:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About that lady there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:33.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you noticed it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.80,0:18:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something's weird, but I can't figure out what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This person... something just isn't right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of weird, don't you think the\N second victim's clothes are weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This lady was attacked as she was\N leaving a park restroom, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.78,0:19:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We took that picture right after\N we arrived at the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.87,0:19:06.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.00,0:19:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The restroom is even in the background.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:14.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since a passerby was the one who found\N her, she must have been alone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if so, why is it she has a\N man's coat on her shoulders?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.67,0:19:21.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's the coat I loaned her at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She seemed to be freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.39,0:19:27.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why was she wearing such light\N clothes in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.93,0:19:30.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She didn't say anything about the\N attacker stealing her coat or anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of which, we haven't had time to take her statement since she's still in a state of shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:45.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you know it's fashionable\N for girls not to wear much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what she wore was sleeveless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:52.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd be too cold for anyone to bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:58.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe she was somewhere warm and had planned\N to go back there after going to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.96,0:20:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere warm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:01.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.97,0:20:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.59,0:20:05.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inside her car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.18,0:20:06.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her car?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, the first and third victims were\N attacked right after they left their cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:16.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then, the fourth happened in a parking garage.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These cases all involve cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.90,0:20:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.73,0:20:23.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi-kun, go contact the second\N victim immediately to confirm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.70,0:20:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean the owner's no longer suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.75,0:20:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:44.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your continued perseverance, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.55,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Matsumoto Kiyonaga (54)\NPolice Headquarters - Superintendent
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent Matsumoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:48.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pleasure to see you again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.97,0:20:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The press has already started reporting that \Nthis is the beginning of a serial murder spree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I advise you pull back for now and start \Nthe investigation anew tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:07.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We already know the girls were\N in their cars before the attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just disguise as a ganguro\Nand act as a decoy in my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:13.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No more decoys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Superintendent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.55,0:21:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, allow us to investigate just a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.88,0:21:26.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure we're getting somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.89,0:21:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I have a feeling that the culprit\N is still around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you must
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.27,0:21:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be that you're still thinking\N back to that case from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:49.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what it is you hide away under your hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.17,0:22:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.80,0:22:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry I asked.
